Package: shadowdom
Type: Package
Title: Create HTML Components With Isolated Formatting
Version: 0.1.0
Imports: htmltools, knitr, utils
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joe", "Cheng", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "joe@rstudio.com"),
    person("RStudio", role = c("cph"))
    )
Description: Allows htmltools-based content to be easily rendered inside of a
    Shadow DOM, which prevents CSS rules declared outside of it from affecting
    HTML content inside of it.
